Writing a large number of passwords on a piece of paper doesn't seem to be 
a good idea to me.

There is an interesting proposal of MATSUMOTO and IMAI to solve the
remote login problem:

MATSUMOTO, IMAI: "Human Identification through Insecure Channel",
		Proceedings of EUROCRYPT '91, Springer.



